{%- comment -%}
  Sha Homepage — templates/index.liquid
  Drop into /templates/index.liquid in your Shopify theme.
  Styles, font imports, BMC widget all live in theme.liquid gated to {% if template contains 'index' %}.
{%- endcomment -%}

<!-- ═══════════════ HERO ═══════════════ -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-kicker">Entrepreneur · Journalist · Technologist</div>
    <h1 class="hero-hed">I build so people have more control over their time, money, &amp; choices.</h1>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-sub">Founder of UpCube. Investigative journalist. Author. New York.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#upcube" class="btn btn-primary">Explore My Work →</a>
      <a href="https://shadabchow.com/blogs/breaking-news" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the Investigations</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="stat-block">
      <div class="stat-num">500M+</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">Video Views Across Platforms</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-foot">0 venture dollars. Built from conviction.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════ STORY ═══════════════ -->
<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="story-inner">
    <div class="label rv">Background</div>
    <h2 class="story-hed rv d1">"My path wasn't linear."</h2>
    <p class="story-body rv d2">Early in life, I made choices that led to four years in a medium-security federal prison. It was violent, tense, and humbling — an environment that stripped away ego and demanded daily courage. That season became a turning point. I learned the cost of wasted potential and the power of second chances. I walked out with a different definition of success: not applause, but alignment. Not noise, but impact. Not reputation, but responsibility.</p>
    <blockquote class="story-pull rv d3">"Today, that conviction fuels everything I do."</blockquote>
    <p class="story-close rv d4">This is not a redemption story. It's a responsibility story.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ UPCUBE ═══════════════ -->
<section class="upcube-section" id="upcube">
  <div class="inner">

    <!-- header -->
    <div class="uc-header rv">
      <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:16px;">What I'm Building</div>
      <div class="uc-brand-row">
        <img
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0799/4369/6609/files/ChatGPT_Image_May_22_2026_12_11_53_AM.png?v=1780440019"
          alt="UpCube"
          class="uc-logo-img"
          width="48"
          height="48"
        >
        <div class="uc-name">UpCube</div>
      </div>
      <p class="uc-manifesto">A technology company building the infrastructure people need to think, create, and act — without asking permission from platforms that weren't built for them. We don't optimize for engagement. We build for ownership, clarity, and long-term leverage.</p>
      <a href="https://upcube.ai" class="uc-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit UpCube.ai →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- technology domains -->
    <div class="uc-domains rv d1">
      <div class="uc-domain">
        <div class="uc-domain-num">01</div>
        <div class="uc-domain-name">Intelligence</div>
        <p class="uc-domain-body">AI systems that reason, research, and act — not just respond. Built to understand context, surface truth, and operate autonomously on behalf of the people using them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-domain">
        <div class="uc-domain-num">02</div>
        <div class="uc-domain-name">Infrastructure</div>
        <p class="uc-domain-body">Cloud compute, virtual machines, and OS-level architecture owned end-to-end. The foundation that everything else runs on — and the layer most companies rent rather than build.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-domain">
        <div class="uc-domain-num">03</div>
        <div class="uc-domain-name">Commerce</div>
        <p class="uc-domain-body">A marketplace architecture built around the buyer, not the advertiser. Where discovery is honest, pricing is transparent, and sellers don't owe a cut to an algorithm.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-domain">
        <div class="uc-domain-num">04</div>
        <div class="uc-domain-name">Knowledge</div>
        <p class="uc-domain-body">Education, publishing, and research tools that distribute insight without a paywall. If understanding something matters, access to it shouldn't depend on a subscription.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="uc-domain">
        <div class="uc-domain-num">05</div>
        <div class="uc-domain-name">Autonomy</div>
        <p class="uc-domain-body">Robotics, voice, and agent systems designed for the physical world. The next layer of human leverage isn't software — it's systems that move, speak, and operate without constant oversight.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- research horizon -->
    <div class="uc-horizon rv d2">
      <div class="uc-horizon-label">Research Horizon</div>
      <p class="uc-horizon-body">Longer term, the research program extends into AGI, quantum computing, biotech, and nanotechnology — not as moonshots, but as responsible bets on what matters in twenty years. The work happening now is the foundation those programs will need.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ JOURNALISM ═══════════════ -->
<section class="journalism" id="journalism">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="label rv">Investigations</div>
    <p class="j-hed rv d1">I follow the facts wherever they lead — and publish what platforms would prefer to throttle.</p>
    <div class="j-beats rv d2">
      <div class="j-beat">
        <div class="j-beat-tag">Crime</div>
        <div class="j-beat-title">Street-level truth, documented.</div>
        <p class="j-beat-body">Reporting that goes where official records don't. Sourced. On the ground. Unedited by algorithm.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="j-beat">
        <div class="j-beat-tag">Corruption</div>
        <div class="j-beat-title">Power under scrutiny.</div>
        <p class="j-beat-body">Contracts, institutions, and systems that fail quietly — exposed in public, with receipts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="j-beat">
        <div class="j-beat-tag">Justice</div>
        <div class="j-beat-title">The system, examined honestly.</div>
        <p class="j-beat-body">From courtrooms to policy rooms — who gets accountability, who doesn't, and why.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="j-foot rv d3">
      <span class="j-note">Published free. No algorithm decides what you see.</span>
      <a href="https://shadabchow.com/blogs/breaking-news" class="j-cta">→ Read All Investigations</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ FREE RESOURCES ═══════════════ -->
<section class="resources" id="resources">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="res-inner">
      <div class="label rv">Free Resources</div>
      <p class="res-quote rv d1">"Too many course sellers charge thousands for recycled advice."</p>
      <div class="res-chips rv d2">
        <a href="#" class="chip">Free Ebooks</a>
        <a href="#" class="chip">Open Datasets</a>
        <a href="#" class="chip">Free Courses</a>
      </div>
      <p class="res-close rv d3">If I can teach it clearly and responsibly, I'd rather put it in your hands for free.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ CONTACT ═══════════════ -->
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="contact-solo rv">
      <div class="label">Reach Out</div>
      <h2 class="contact-hed">"If you have a lead, a collaboration, or a problem worth solving — reach out."</h2>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn-primary contact-btn">Get in Touch →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>